Description

ApplicationController
Handles application-related operations such as applying for BTO, requesting withdrawals, and viewing application status.
ApplicationMain
Provides the user interface for application-related tasks such as: - Officer: booking flats, generating receipts - Manager: approving/rejecting applications and withdrawals, filtering Implements IApplicationMain.

Represents the status of an applicant's application to a BTO Project
BTOApplication
Represents a BTO (Build-To-Order) application submitted by an applicant.

Defines ANSI escape codes for coloring console output.
Enquiry

EnquiryController class manages all operations related to enquiries in the BTO system.

EnquiryStatus
Represents the status of an enquiry
